Class Windows

java.lang.Object
main.java.com.team.game.ui.Windows
public final class Windows extends Object
Centralized factory for opening all application windows.

This class standardizes how new JavaFX stages are created and displayed. Each method ensures the JavaFX runtime is active, loads the appropriate FXML view, sets dependencies (e.g. GameService, User), and opens the scene on the JavaFX Application Thread.
